dc_description_s: Map of Mountain Lakes, New Jersey removed from the League of Women Voters' "Know Your Town", 1967 edition. Legend shows designations for residential, business and economic development zones. Map was funded through a U.S. grant from the Urban Renewal Administration of the Housing and Home Finance Agency and an appropriation from the expanded New Jersey State and Regional Planning Program.
